headline: Countdown to Chipotle (CMG) Q1 Earnings: Wall Street Forecasts for Key Metrics
summary: Get a deeper insight into the potential performance of Chipotle (CMG) for the quarter ended March 2025 by going beyond Wall Street's top -and-bottom-line estimates and examining the estimates for some of its key metrics.
